id: rollout_progress
type: custom
order: after sites
title: Rollout Progress
slide_type: custom
data_tools: [customer_sites, customer_health]
customers: ["Siemens"]

prompt: |
  This slide is specific to Siemens and tracks their multi-site rollout.
  Categorize each site into a stage: Live (active users in the last 7 days),
  Training (has a training site with recent activity), Onboarding (users
  exist but activity is minimal), and Not Started (no users or no activity).

  Show a progress bar or count of sites in each stage. Compare current
  state to the previous period if possible. The goal is to give the CSM
  a clear picture of rollout velocity — are new sites coming online on
  schedule or is the rollout stalling?
